'''Aldo Fiorelli''' (1915–1983) was an Italian [[actor]] who appeared in around thirty films between 1938 and 1960. One of his final roles was Argos, the Shipbuilder in the 1958 film ''[[Hercules (1958 film)|Hercules]]''<ref>Hughes p.2</ref> and its 1959 sequel ''[[Hercules Unchained]]''.

